OL,3,CCampaigners beat fundraising target to
OL,4,Ctransform abandoned flats into housing
OL,6,FCampaigners in Looe are celebrating
OL,7,Fafter raising just enough money to
OL,8,Fturn a row of abandoned coastguard
OL,9,Fflats into affordable housing.
OL,11,FThree Seas, the not-for-profit
OL,12,Forganisation selling community shares
OL,13,Ffor the 11 historic flats, had to
OL,14,Fraise #100,000 by midnight on Friday
OL,15,F31 May.
OL,17,FBy Thursday morning, the group still
OL,18,Fhad #30,000 to go but told ITV West
OL,19,FCountry they were "confident" they
OL,20,Fwould achieve their target.
