OL,3,CCampaigners beat fundraising target to
OL,4,Ctransform abandoned flats into housing
OL,6,FThey have now confirmed they have
OL,7,Fpassed their target "by just a
OL,8,Fridiculously small margin". After
OL,9,Fcounting up the card donations,
OL,10,Fcheques and bank transfers, Three Seas
OL,11,Fsaid they managed to raise #100,300 by
OL,12,Fmidnight on Friday.
OL,14,F"I'm completely shocked", said Simon
OL,15,FRyan, the manager of the campaign.
OL,17,F"It's obviously a massive sense of
OL,18,Frelief for the group around the town.
OL,19,FIt couldn't be any tighter though", he
OL,20,Fadded.
