OL,3,CCampaigners beat fundraising target to
OL,4,Ctransform abandoned flats into housing
OL,6,FMembers of the local community
OL,7,Fcontinued to donate right up until the
OL,8,Flast minute, according to Simon.
OL,10,FWhile the group shut their office at
OL,11,F5pm on Friday, 31 people donated a
OL,12,Ftotal of around #4,000 after that
OL,13,Fpoint.
OL,15,F"I knew people would pay in late, you
OL,16,Fknow, nine thirty and afterwards",
OL,17,FSimon said.
OL,19,F"We did it by just a ridiculously
OL,20,Fsmall margin - but we've made #200,000
OL,21,Ffor Looe! A massive win for the town!"
