OL,3,CCampaigners beat fundraising target to
OL,4,Ctransform abandoned flats into housing
OL,6,FThe deadline for the fundraising
OL,7,Ftarget was because the money raised in
OL,8,Fcommunity shares would be matched by a
OL,9,Fgrant, pound for pound, if they
OL,10,Fachieved the target by the deadline.
OL,11,FIt means there is now #200,000
OL,12,Favailable for Three Seas to refurbish
OL,13,Fthe dilapidated interiors of the
OL,14,Fproperties and turn them into
OL,15,Faffordable housing.
